&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span style="color:red;font-family:cursive"&gt;hello&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;p style="text-align:center"&gt;
  centered paragraph
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;


&lt;div style="text-align:center"&gt;centered div&lt;/div&gt;

- unordered list 1
- unordered list 5
- unordered list 3


1. ordered list 1
2. ordered list 2
3. ordered list 3

![my image](/image.jpg "my image")
        </label>
      </input>
    </group>
  </h:body>
</h:html>
